description: With Quirky's Wrapster, you can say good-bye to tangled earbud headphones - we've created the ultimate cord management solution! The Wrapster’s unique design allows you to wrap your cords vertically, which means more convenience and less bulk. With the Wrapster, you’ll finally be able to wrangle the tangle out of your earbud headphones.
title: Quirky Wrapster for Headphone (Charcoal)
